ERROR:  key join alias "t2" is not present in the left join operand
LINE 1: ...self_syntax AS t1 JOIN key_join_self_syntax AS t2 FOR KEY (p...
                                                             ^
SELECT * FROM key_join_self_syntax AS t1 JOIN key_join_self_syntax AS t2 FOR KEY (id) <- t1 (parent_id); -- accepted
 id | parent_id | id | parent_id 
