ERROR:  key join column lists must have the same length
LINE 1: SELECT * FROM t1 JOIN t2 FOR KEY (c3, c4) -> t1 (c1, c2, c3)...
                                 ^
-- rejected, reason: referencing column c5 does not exist
SELECT * FROM t1 JOIN t2 FOR KEY (c3, c4, c5) -> t1 (c1, c2);
ERROR:  key join column lists must have the same length
LINE 1: SELECT * FROM t1 JOIN t2 FOR KEY (c3, c4, c5) -> t1 (c1, c2)...
